Usage: relink_db_files [-help] -db_dir <db_dir>
                       -new_lib_dirs {<new_lib_dir1> <new_lib_dir2> ...}

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-db_dir <db_dir>     # The current db directory which contains incorrect
                     # library symbolic links. (string, required)
-new_lib_dirs {<new_lib_dir1> <new_lib_dir2> ...}
                     # The new directories to search for library files (string, required)